{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"History.state","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/state","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History_API\">History API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/length\"><code>length</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/scrollRestoration\"><code>scrollRestoration</code></a></li><li><em><code>state</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methods</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/back\"><code>back()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/forward\"><code>forward()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/go\"><code>go()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/pushState\"><code>pushState()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/replaceState\"><code>replaceState()</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><span class=\"seoSummary\"><strong><code>History.state</code></strong>&nbsp;속성은 현 history에 해당하는 state값을 나타냅니다.</span></p>\n\n<p><code><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/Window/popstate_event\" title=\"/ko/docs/Web/Reference/Events/popstate\">popstate</a></code> 이벤트가 트리거될때가 아닌 상태에서 state값을 볼 수 있는 방법입니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"구문","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">const <em>currentState</em> = history.state</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"value","title":"값","isH3":true,"content":"<p>현 history에 위치한 값입니다. 이 값은 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/pushState\" title=\"pushState()\"><code>pushState()</code></a>&nbsp;또는 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/replaceState\" title=\"replaceState()\"><code>replaceState()</code></a>을 사용할때까지 <a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Operators/null\"><code>null</code></a> 값을 가집니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"예제","isH3":false,"content":"<p><code>history.state</code>&nbsp;로 초기값을 보여준 후&nbsp;<a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/pushState\" title=\"pushState()\"><code>pushState()</code></a>를 사용하여 State를 푸시합니다.</p>\n\n<p>다음 코드 줄은&nbsp;<code>history.state</code>&nbsp;를 사용하여 콘솔에다 값이 푸시되었음을 보여줍니다.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token comment\">// Should be null because we haven't modified the history stack yet</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">History.state before pushState: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Now push something on the stack</span>\nhistory<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pushState</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span><span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Example'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"pushState example\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'page3.html'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Now state has a value.</span>\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span><span class=\"token string\">History.state after pushState: </span><span class=\"token interpolation\"><span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">${</span>history<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>state<span class=\"token interpolation-punctuation punctuation\">}</span></span><span class=\"token template-punctuation string\">`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"명세","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#dom-history-state\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'History.state' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Living Standard</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/html52/browsers.html#dom-history-state\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5<br><small lang=\"ko\">The definition of 'History.state' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-rec\">Recommendation</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"브라우저 호환성","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.History.state","dataURL":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/state/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"같이 보기","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/History_API/Working_with_the_History_API\">Working with the History API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"구문","id":"syntax"},{"text":"예제","id":"examples"},{"text":"명세","id":"specifications"},{"text":"브라우저 호환성","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"같이 보기","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"History.state 속성은 현 history에 해당하는 state값을 나타냅니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"History.state","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"History.state","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"History.state","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"state","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/web/api/history/state","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/web/api/history/state/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web","title":"개발자를 위한 웹 기술"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History","title":"History"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Web/API/History/state","title":"History.state"}],"pageTitle":"History.state - Web API | MDN","noIndexing":false}}